<h2 class="nounderline"><a name="maincontentlink">Improving Family-School Communication</a></h2>


<!--BEGIN CONTENT-->

<p>
Improving family-school communication is the foundation for successful parental involvement.  Clear and appropriate communication with families is the basic responsibility of the school.  The more that parents and teachers are able to share information with each other about students, the more they can work tog</p>
<p>ether to help those students become successful. </p>
